Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.21,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.05,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.71,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,今日もいい天気です
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.41,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ほんとだね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.54,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ポチ　今日の予定って何だっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.32,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,お昼まではお好きに過ごしてください
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.22,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,昼食はポンタローさんが同席の予定です
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.31,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ポンタロー
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.32,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ん　分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.96,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,他には誰か来ない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.04,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.47,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,ここには誰も来ませんから　大丈夫です
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.94,0:00:39.48,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.48,0:00:40.93,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,朝ごはんにしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.15,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,8時半になったら学校行かなくちゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.32,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.47,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,それでは先にお着替えをお済ませください
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.23,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,宿題したっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.34,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,なさいました
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.75,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.25,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ありがとう　ポチ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.25,0:00:54.92,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.45,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.38,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Comment: 1,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.75,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.44,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お　葉香姫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.40,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,いつにもまして
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.46,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お顔色もよろしくクールアンドセクシーでいらっしゃる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.32,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.51,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,私のような下賤なものにもお声がけ下さるとは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.66,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,このポイズン・ポンタロー　恭悦の極み
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.81,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,つまり最大級に光栄だということです
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.93,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,お昼ご飯　何
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.71,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,鹹さ10倍カレーと
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.42,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,吾野さんゴヤーの酢のものでございます
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.29,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.73,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,このような田舎料理
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.92,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香姫のお口に合わないかもしれませんね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.39,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,要するに　作り直せということだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.26,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ジャストナウ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.91,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,食べるよ　ゴーヤ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.48,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,でもなんでゴーヤ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.44,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,保谷経由で仕入れました
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.95,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,キャラバン隊から持ち込まれたものだそうです
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.02,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.27,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.58,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,あいやいやいや
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.27,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ポチ君　いつもご苦労様
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.66,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ポチ君とは不祥のポンタローと同じ　「ポ」始まり「ポ」同値
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.67,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫に忠誠を尽くして参りましょうではありませんか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.79,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そうを努めております
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.73,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,もうポチッチってば姫のことしか考えてないんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.03,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可愛い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.17,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そっちも食うが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.37,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,を　もちろんです
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.42,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,あもちもち
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.55,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.84,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,えっど
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.57,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ゴンタローさん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.17,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ポンタローですはいはい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.41,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,トンタローさんって誰なんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.02,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.24,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,よく遊びに来るじゃないですか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.67,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんでだろうって思って
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.68,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,嫌だなあもう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.79,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫　お談無理が過ぎますぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.91,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,市の中心をお忘れになるなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.12,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,市長のポイズン・ポンタローです
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.57,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,覚えておいていただかなければ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.18,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,姫とか中心て言うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.89,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ちょっとわかんないっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.66,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私は
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.02,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,何をおっしゃいますやら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.01,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お忘れですか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.31,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫がこの池袋にいらっしゃった時のこと
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.09,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,要するに　池袋で姫をお迎えした時のこと
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,池袋に　来た時
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.61,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫を出迎えたのは私　このポンタローですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.90,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ご記憶にない　何たる悲しみ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.90,0:04:53.11,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,より専門的な言葉を用いることを許していただけるのであれば
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.38,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,やはり悲しいということなのです
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.54,JP-Main-Down,Man 1,0,0,0,,あの娘が
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.67,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,間違いない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.27,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,トリガになりやがったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.57,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,持ち物見たら中富葉香っていうらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.77,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,吾野とやらに住んでる高校生だ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.33,JP-Main-Down,Man 2,0,0,0,,こんなことになるなら
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.27,JP-Main-Down,Man 2,0,0,0,,奴らの忠告を聞いておくんだった
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.27,0:05:13.89,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,わうい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.23,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,すべてが想定内だったということにしておけ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.16,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,今更7Gは失敗でしたなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.42,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,口は裂けても言えるかってんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.96,JP-Main-Down,Man 1,0,0,0,,元に戻す方法を
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.14,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,おいおいおいおい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.82,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,責任なんて取れるかっつの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.64,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,しらばくれてここは現状維持で行くぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.93,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,知ってるのは誰もいねし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.84,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,まあいることはいるけどそいつパートし大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.86,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,この女さえうまくやっときゃいいだけの話だ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.86,0:05:31.38,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,いいか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.06,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,絶対に目を離すんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.13,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,わかりました
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.91,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ちょっとでもミスったら　餌抜きだかんな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.47,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.71,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.29,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.00,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私何してたんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.94,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんかぼやぼやする
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.11,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そろそろ起きましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.98,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんて
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.20,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,散歩をしなくてはいけません
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.21,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,うんこすることも大事だと言われました
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.39,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,早く　起きてください
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.09,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,散歩に行きましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.98,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ぽっちさんみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.91,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,ポチ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.89,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,散歩が好きで　いつも一緒にいる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.51,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,家で飼ってる大きな犬
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.84,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,それに強くて優しいんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.27,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.43,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,では私を「ポチ」と呼んでください
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.18,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,いつも一緒にいます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.63,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,大きな体になりました
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.31,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,多分強いです
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.64,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,飛んだりすることは今となっては難しくなってしまいましたが
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.01,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,それは大きな問題ではありません
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.27,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,でもあなた
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.80,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,私はポチ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.46,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,散歩に行きましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ここが池袋
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.54,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そうらしいです
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.40,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.95,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんか　思ってたのと違うみたいな感じ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.40,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,こんならしいです
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.76,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,思ってた以上にすごいみたいな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.75,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,思っててよりつまんないみたいな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.11,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,でもこれからはもっと栄えるかもしれません
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.11,0:06:56.84,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,もっと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.74,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.74,0:07:01.87,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,なぜならば池袋には葉香様がいらっしゃるからです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.09,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,関係なくない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.56,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,あると聞きました
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.56,0:07:12.45,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,今の池袋は葉香様がすごく関係しています
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.43,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.43,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,やっぱり錆びれてるより栄えてた方がいいものね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.40,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.10,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,どうせならもっと高くもっと大きく
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.77,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,空ももっと近く美しく
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.45,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,やっぱり街はいいね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.25,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,賑やかだと気持ちも上がるし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.76,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,静かだと気持ちも落ち込みますか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.30,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静かだと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.63,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静かな時に何かあると
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.22,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,落ち込むっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.96,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静かでもいいんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.98,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,え　いや　えっとどうだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.87,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,とにかく都会もいいってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.02,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,はい　そうです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.37,0:08:00.27,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,先日私の部下に渋谷新宿上野あたりを探索に行かせましたが
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.94,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,見つかりませんでした
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.58,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,え　大変
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.18,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,しかし　池袋は姫のご意向によって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.75,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,絶好調にして万事順調であります
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.65,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ダークマター
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.17,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.13,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,てまだ見つかってないんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.20,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.20,0:08:13.84,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ポチ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.59,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,一応発見されたと言われているのはニュートリノですね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.26,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あれは暗黒物質じゃないんじゃなかったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.76,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,誰だっけ見つけた人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.20,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あ　あの人だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.67,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,テレビゲームつきの人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.44,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ゲーム
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.91,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,テレビゲーム
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.56,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ゲームはともかく
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.12,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.12,0:08:34.13,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋にあだなそうとする潜入者どもがおります
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.13,0:08:34.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あだなす
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.43,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.94,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界がおかしいだの変だのケチをつける奴らです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.74,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,出たの魔女め
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.83,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,消えてしまった世界を返せ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.07,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,返せって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.53,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,よくわからないんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.83,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,何もかも全部消しやがって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.42,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,私が消した
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.42,0:08:51.79,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.82,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,恍けるね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.71,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,お前とお前の起こした7G事件のせいで
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.46,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,世界はめちゃくちゃだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.05,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あなたはこの世界が嫌いなの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.77,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,好き嫌いの問題じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.81,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,でもめちゃくちゃって思ってるんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.41,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,なんたる不敬
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.44,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫のご意向に逆らう貴公
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.54,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,煩い
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.91,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,なんで他の路線が犠牲にならないといけないんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.34,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.29,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,何も犠牲になんかなってない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.74,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,前からこのまま
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.40,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そしてこれからもこのまま
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.63,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,このままなんぞまっぴらだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.43,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,前の世界に戻す
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.82,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そんな世界なんて知らない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.25,JP-Main-up-8,Pontaro,0,0,0,,そうだ　ない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.47,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,あるわけがない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.47,0:09:31.00,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,お前の力は知ってるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.64,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,池袋の魔女
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.50,JP-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,お前が作った池袋などまがいものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.62,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,噓月
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.68,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.87,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,奴らは勝手な思い込みをしているんです
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.32,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,前の世界など元からなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.56,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,それをあったことにして
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.79,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,よりにもよって姫のせいにしている
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.64,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お　お　これは
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,陰謀の匂いがペンペンするぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.07,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,よろしい殺さす
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.26,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,思い知ったかこの茶碗蒸しやろう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.01,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫に逆らうとこうなるのだ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.88,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,要するに熱熱も面白い
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.59,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,熱熱
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.59,0:10:05.62,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,熱いそこの野郎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.32,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ああ　未だ食べちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.36,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,戻りましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.46,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,ここは風が強いです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.72,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんであの人はこの世界が嫌いなのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.80,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,なぜでしょう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.83,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,楽しいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.64,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香様が楽しいと思えるのであれば
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.20,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,私も楽しいです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,楽しい　いのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.45,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,楽しいってなんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.72,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ポチ　ちょっといいかな
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.83,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あのもンタローとかって人ちょっと苦手
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.56,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,ちょっと外します
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.24,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,誰がお前を助けてやったか忘れるんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.33,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,名無しの朴念仁の唐変木
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.33,0:10:45.04,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,私がいなければお前なんぞ負け者クラブの一員だ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.58,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,言いたいことはそれだけか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.45,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,役目を果たせ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.45,0:10:51.17,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近妙に感情が不安定になることがある
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.23,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,あれに何か少しでも異常があればすぐに知らせろこの私にだ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.34,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,わかっている
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.31,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,本当にわかってんのか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.09,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,もし裏切るようなことがあれば
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.17,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,その時は茶碗蒸しどころじゃないからな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.96,0:11:10.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんか池袋線じゃないみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.00,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なにを今更
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.09,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,こんな景色お父さんやお母さんに見せたらびっくりするんだろうな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.03,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,するかな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.47,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,案外平レベルだったりするかもよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん家って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.24,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,お父さんはハダカデバネズミで
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.25,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,お母さんがキノボリカンガルーだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.88,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん　おじいちゃんは三葉虫
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.20,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あ　やばい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.28,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,図書館の本返却してなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.34,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,延滞だね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.20,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どうせまた変な本でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,誰も借りないから大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.42,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,駄目だよ玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.76,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そういうことじゃないから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.03,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やばいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ほら静留ちゃんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,食べかけのお弁当箱そのままにしてきた気がする
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.63,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,多分布団の上か　中
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.88,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嫌だ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「中」ってどういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんか　そのまま
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,きっとお母さんがなんとかしてくれてるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.19,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうそう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,レッサーパンダって食べる前に洗うんだもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.60,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それはアライグマでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.69,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,レッサーパンダって洗わないんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.93,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,料理する時とか食器はちゃんと洗ってたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあ大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.52,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何そのオプチミズム
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.80,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,楽観主義ってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶だってなんとかしてくれるって言ってたじゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.48,JP-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,それはそうだけど…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.24,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,誰かが　なんとか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.29,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ありがとうね付き合ってくれて
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.05,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何　いきなり
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.67,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,びっくりしたもう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.62,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いや　なんとなく
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.23,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,付き合いできたんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.73,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,行きたいと思ったから来たんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.41,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん　結構楽しいし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,帰ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.48,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,21歳と3ヶ月になる前に
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.98,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,旅行記まとめなきゃだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ読む読む
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.76,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,つか私も出るんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,出さざるを得ないね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,むっちゃかっこよく書いてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,強くて美人で賢いて　みちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.68,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ちゃんと真実を書かなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.32,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真実って全部真実じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,まあでも　ちゃんと吾野に帰れるかどうかだな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.43,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋にうついちゃったり
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それはないか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.72,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.83,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,まあ　可能性がないとは言えないけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.57,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.76,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,帰ろうよ　葉香ちゃんと一緒に
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.83,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,みんな待ってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.05,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.40,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,待ってるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.40,0:13:03.80,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.65,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんだろうあれ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.21,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,仙人　スワンボートの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.34,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,地図くれたおじいさん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.51,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あの怪しい奴
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.41,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ね　あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やばくない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.05,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ミスってる
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.86,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いやいやいやいや
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.23,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,何か　うまく
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.33,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,みんな退いて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.33,0:13:31.88,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんロープ持ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.41,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　わかった
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.66,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何　撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.22,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電車止めて静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,オーケー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.67,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.71,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,いけ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,やれやれ死ぬかと思った
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.59,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋線を遡っていったんじゃなかったの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.87,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで池袋の方から
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.40,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,いや　こっちは吾野を超え
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.61,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,吾野のおく西吾野を目指して
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.70,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,西へ西へと向かっていたはずだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.54,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.52,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも池袋方面から来たよ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.52,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どこかで大曲りしてたとこ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.27,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そんなはずは
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,あるやもしれん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.01,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,地図を見せてみろ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.27,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,前に私がくれてやった地図だ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どこやったっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,知らない
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.01,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あった
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.67,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,扱いざずすぎが
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.44,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だって書いてあるのが曖昧すぎるんだも
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.62,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ヘタウマ風味でね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.68,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,この地図は
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.01,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,現状唯一世界の様相を示したものなんだぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.18,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,英知の結晶だ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.86,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,覚えているか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.56,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,初めてあったのはここ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.90,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一方今はここだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.72,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うん　そうなんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これってもしかして東吾野の茸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.27,0:14:48.76,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.07,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でこれは武蔵横手の山羊人間
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.80,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これは稲荷山の小さい人たち
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ひょっとしてのひょっとしてだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.80,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ネリアリの混沌
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.74,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地図合ってたってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.70,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,言っただろう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.94,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,英知の結晶だと
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,スワンボートでのんびり旅してる人が
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.10,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そんなにのすみのことまで知ってるとは思わないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.10,0:15:10.12,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,ではなぜ人類は134億光年彼方にある
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.17,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,銀河について知り得たのだと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.48,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　なんでだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.64,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,探究心で探究心
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.75,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そして冷静な観察力
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.55,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,私は探究心に駆られてひたすら高麗川を遡ったのだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ　そんな話してたっけね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.60,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そして今日なぜかここで再会した
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.41,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,実に興味深い事情だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,知らない間に戻ってきたんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.38,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あるある　自分がやってたこと忘れちゃうの
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,年取ると脳みそ古びてくるから
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.87,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.18,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,私の脳みそに乱れはない
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.88,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,乱れているとしたらそれは　この世界の方だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.77,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,あ　何を今更という顔をしたなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.96,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,茸に似非巨人にゾンビに
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.14,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,たいことがした高麗川
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.63,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,確かに世界は大きく変化した
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.87,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,だが私が言いたいのは　今もなお続く変化のことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.12,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっとなお続く変化って
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.97,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界はを収縮し　池袋は膨張し
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.56,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界の法則は今命の道を深めておる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.73,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あんまり難しいこと言われても
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.23,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,膨張ってそれ　反映の今違う
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.85,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,違う　膨張だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.26,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋が歪に膨れ上がっているのだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.13,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,気持ち悪い言い方するね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.05,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,膨れ上がった後はどうなるんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.05,0:16:15.93,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,消える
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.80,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それって池袋が　吾野は
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.21,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,全部消える
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,止められないの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.11,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.11,0:16:22.90,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,断言
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.90,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,事実だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.19,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ていうかさ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,街には偉い人たちがいるんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんて何もしてくれないんだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,偉い人いるのかなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,考えたこともなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.17,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,駄目だよ　ちゃんと考えないと
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.17,0:16:35.98,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,無駄だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.88,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,手を打つきがあるならとっくに打っているだろうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.30,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それもそっか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,結局自分でどうにかするしかないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.23,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,ねそれはどうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.65,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.34,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,混乱してしまったこの世界をどうにかさせないという力が
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.14,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋に存在する気がしてならない
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.53,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,お前たちが池袋に向かうとなると
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.13,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,その恐ろしい力と対峙することになるやもしれんぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.86,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,その覚悟はあるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.37,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,私にはない
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.47,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,動くな　おとなしくしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.09,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,帽子どこだ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.60,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,手荒れ郵便局に響く
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.49,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,目薬ぽちょんとご参照
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.09,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,やっぱりいつもの帽子でないと駄目なのか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.80,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ポンタローのうにゃうにゃ手術は
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.84,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,これ以上回復不可能ってことか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.00,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,え　待て
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.89,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G暴走止めないと　池袋すら消える
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.25,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gのおおもとを突き止め
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.53,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,壊れた世界を修復しなければナラない
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.53,0:17:33.15,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,そしてポンタローのさらなる企みを粉砕し
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.85,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,阻止する必要がある
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.91,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,少し戻ってきた
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.15,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,いやまで
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.08,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,池袋が消えるとはどういうことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.91,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,エントロピーの増大
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.47,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,宇宙の膨張のミニマナバン
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.48,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ビッグリップ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.20,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,シャボン玉消えた
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.90,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,壊れて消えた
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.79,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,原理はともかく消滅はいつ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.90,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ボボー
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.11,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,分からんの
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.62,0:18:00.10,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,明日かもしれないし　20億年後かもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.72,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,誰も予測できない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.21,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.80,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,君は技術者とも思えない発言をするな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.99,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,わかったわかった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.23,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,どうどうどうどう
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.48,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,膨張消滅が　避けられないことだとしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.95,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もう冒険はいいんじゃないですか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうだよ危ないよ仙人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.28,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,馬鹿を言うな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.48,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,今もこれからも世界は変わり続けるんだぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.29,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,それを見ずしてどうする
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.38,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無茶苦茶だ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.95,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人生なんぞいつだって無茶苦茶なもんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.95,0:18:31.22,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,仙人って7Gの前から無茶苦茶な人生だったの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.22,0:18:31.80,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.65,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一言で言って　めっちゃめちゃのグッチョグッチョだった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.51,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋で何あったとひと
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.88,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そういうことは聞かないのが大人というものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.32,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,英知の決勝改訂版だ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,新しい地図
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.06,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.09,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,お前たちが池袋に向かうのならば力となるだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.60,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあこれ地図のお返し
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.31,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,持ってきなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.94,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,たちはさ　これからも食べ物ありそうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,仙人は多分やばいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これも
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.49,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,これから行くところが寒くないって保証はないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.35,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,それでは遠慮なく
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.30,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,つってまた明日あたりばったりあったりしてね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.69,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,それもありえる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.08,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世の中に確かなことなど一つもない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.70,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,気をつけてね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.55,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,それはお前たちの方だ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.55,0:19:11.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.33,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,膨張した池袋が安全で反映していると思ったら大間違いだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.35,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,逆だ逆
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.85,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,住人は出ていけないからそこに封じられている
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.88,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,私がこうしているのは運が良かっただけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.76,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋の魔女王は深淵そのものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,深淵
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.47,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,彼女は謎と道と恐怖で成り立っている
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.31,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋の魔女って　葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.31,0:19:38.83,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そんな名前だった気がしないでもないが忘れた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.64,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香は悪いことなんかしないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.46,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人は変わる　世界も変わる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.72,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,ずっと同じものがあるか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.70,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あるよ…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.19,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.13,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,しかしそれは同じに見えているだけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.63,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,変わらないとすれば
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それは同じところに留まるべく動き続けているから
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.33,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,その通り
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.72,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,永遠や不滅など存在しない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで最後に嫌なこと言うかな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.38,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,では忘れらろ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.38,0:20:04.94,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,無理
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.89,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,もう聞いちゃったも
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.97,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,変貌を知りたい私と
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.47,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不滅を取り戻したいお前たちか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.16,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,これだから面白い
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.40,0:20:18.24,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,面白の故郷の吾野のその先の西吾野を見つけたならば
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.78,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,もしくはひょんなところで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.78,0:20:23.16,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,西部新宿線や東部東上線が見つかったのならば
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.95,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,その時は戻ってくる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.48,JP-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,ではさらば
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.05,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,かっこよく去ってったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.63,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,具体的にどうやって戻る気なんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.29,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんかな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,草餅
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.57,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　美味しそう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.69,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,てことはこっちは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.36,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,カレー
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.42,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でもどんぶりだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,色々調べてるのはわかるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.20,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,映画微妙だよね仙人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,草餅食べたい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.12,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,つぶあん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.22,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え　こしあんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,わかってないなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,つぶあんのがつうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.64,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん　元気かなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,元気でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.10,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ちょっと変だったの気になるけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.43,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,写真の葉香ちゃん　今までと全然違ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.61,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋の魔女って　どういう意味なんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.61,0:21:10.58,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それ何かの間違いだとか誤解だと思ってるよ私　絶対
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.26,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そうそう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.13,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あの音無し葉香ちゃんがだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,魔女なんてありえないって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.46,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もしかして葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.87,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,悪い人たちに巻き込まれてるのかも
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.71,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,何のようだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.71,0:21:32.97,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,大泉学園から知らせが来た
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.97,0:21:36.30,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋に向かっている面倒な虫がいると
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.27,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,どうやら姫の知り合いらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.29,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,もし昔の知り合いなんかにあって記憶が戻ったりしたら大事だ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.29,0:21:46.32,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,一応椎名町では限界体制を敷いているが念には念だ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.07,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,排除できる準備をしておけお
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.22,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,前の務めは姫をお守りすることだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.42,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,わかっている
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.79,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,何してるんだろう私
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.76,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,何で私こんなとこにいるんだろう
Comment: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.37,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.21,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.71,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,今天也是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.41,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.54,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博七 今天預定的安排有哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.32,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,在中午前請按自己喜歡的方式度過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.22,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,午餐已經預定和龐太郎先生一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.31,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.32,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.96,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,沒有其他人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.04,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,沒有人會來到這裡的 請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:39.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:40.93,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,去吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.15,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,八點半就必須得去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.32,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,在這之前請您自行更衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.23,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.34,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.75,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.25,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,謝謝你 博七
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:54.92,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.45,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.38,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,請
Comment: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.75,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,噢 葉香公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.40,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,無論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您的臉色都非常冷靜與感性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.32,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.51,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您連我這樣的卑微之人都願意與其對話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.66,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,芃伊斯·龐太郎我 誠惶誠恐 欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,也就是說 這讓我倍感光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.93,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,午餐 吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.71,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,十倍鹹的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,還有產自吾野的苦瓜製作的涼醋拌菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這種鄉下菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.92,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,很有可能不符合葉香公主的口味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.39,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,總而言之 都給公主重新製作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,立刻馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我能吃的 苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但為什麼是苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是從保谷那裡採購的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.95,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,據說是黑豹商隊運輸來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.27,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,博七君 一直以來都辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.66,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,博七君和不幸的龐太郎一樣 姓同宗氏同源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.67,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,讓我們懷著一顆犬馬之心忠於公主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,正在這樣努力中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真是的博七七心裡只想著公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.03,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,你也吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.37,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哦 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊 軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,混太郎先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是龐太郎 對對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.41,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,桃太郎先生是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你不是經常來這裡玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.67,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我在想為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真是好不喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主 您說得太超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.91,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您忘記了這裡是城市的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.12,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是市長芃伊斯·龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.57,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,要好好記得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.18,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,雖說以公主我為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.89,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但我並不明白為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.66,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您在胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.31,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主剛來池袋時發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,簡而言之 就是當時在池袋迎接公主的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,池袋 我來到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.61,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,出來迎接的人是我 龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您都不記得了 多麼悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:53.11,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果您允許我用更為專業的話語描述
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.38,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真的是痛心疾首啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.54,ZH-Main-Down,Man 1,0,0,0,,那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.67,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她開啟了開關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.57,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,看她隨身攜帶的物件應該是叫中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.77,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是住在吾野的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.33,ZH-Main-Down,Man 2,0,0,0,,早知這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.27,ZH-Main-Down,Man 2,0,0,0,,就聽那群傢伙的忠告了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:13.89,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.23,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,當作「一切都是計劃的一部分」就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.16,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,現在說7G什麼的已經失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就算吃了黃連也只能裝作啞巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.96,ZH-Main-Down,Man 1,0,0,0,,恢復原狀的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.14,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.82,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,私密馬塞都沒你還想承擔責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,別犯傻了 就維持現狀就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這事又沒人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.84,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就算有也都推給臨時工問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.86,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,只要這女的做得好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:31.38,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.06,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,視線絕對不能離開她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.91,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,要有一丁點失誤 就別想著吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.71,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.00,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我在做什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.94,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,感覺迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.11,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是時候起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.98,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.20,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,您必須起來散步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.21,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,排便也是一件很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.39,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,請 快點起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,一起去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.98,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好像波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.91,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.89,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,喜歡散步 經常和我一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我家飼養的大狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,它很強也很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.43,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,那麼請稱呼我為「博七」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.18,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我會一直陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.63,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我的身體較為健碩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.31,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,大概很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,雖然現在飛行是比較難的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,但那並不是大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.27,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是 你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.80,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是博七
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,一起去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這裡是池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.54,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,看起來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.95,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,感覺 和想像中的有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.40,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.76,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,看起來比想像中的更神奇一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.75,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,看起來比想像中的更百無聊賴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.11,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,但是未來很有可能會更加繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:56.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,更加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.74,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:01.87,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,因為池袋有葉香大人在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.09,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.56,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我聽說有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:12.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,現在的池袋和葉香大人具有很強的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.43,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.43,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,果然比起腐鏽 繁榮更加美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.40,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.10,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,既然這樣 就再高點 再大點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.77,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,離天空更近 更美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.45,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,果然「城市」好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.25,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,熱鬧的時候情緒也會高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.76,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,寂靜的時候心情也會失落嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.30,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「靜」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.63,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,寂靜的時候會感覺什麼存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.22,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,應該就是失落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.96,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,雖然寂靜也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.98,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但 不對 到底怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.87,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,總之 大城市也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:08:00.27,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,前幾日我讓部下去澀谷 新宿 上野探索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.94,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.18,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 池袋在公主的指導下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.75,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,經濟蒸蒸日上 人民安居樂業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.65,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,暗物質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.13,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,還沒有見到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.20,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:13.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,暫時已經發現的是微中子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.26,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那種粒子應該不是暗物質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.76,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是誰第一個發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.20,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 是那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,隨身攜帶電視遊戲機的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,電視遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.56,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,先不說遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.12,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:34.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋有一群潛入的「仇人」們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:34.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.43,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.94,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,挑剔世界奇怪而且有問題的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.74,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,出現了魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.83,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,把消失的世界還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.07,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,還什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.53,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我一點也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.83,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,所有的東西都被消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.42,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我 把它們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:51.79,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.82,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,裝什麼傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,因為你 還有你引發的7G事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,世界變得混亂無章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你討厭這個世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.77,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,根本不是喜歡不喜歡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.81,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是你認為這一切都很荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,多麼不敬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.44,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,違背公主意志的愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.91,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,為什麼要犧牲其它鐵路沿線的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.34,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,沒有任何會被犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.74,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,過去就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,而且今後也會如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.63,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,這樣子下去什麼也做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.43,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,快點把原本的世界還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那種世界我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.25,ZH-Main-up-8,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:31.00,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,我知道你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.64,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.50,ZH-Main-Down,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,你所創造的池袋也不過是虛妄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這傢伙只會自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.32,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,以前的世界根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.56,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就算它真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,偏偏把責任都怪罪到公主身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,噢 噢 這可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,陰謀的香味撲面而來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好吧殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,現在你懂了吧 你這碗蛋羹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,違背公主就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.88,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,總之 又燙又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好熱好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:05.62,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你這傢伙太燙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.32,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊啊 幾口就吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.36,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,這裡風很強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.72,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼那個人會討厭這個世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.80,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.83,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不是很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,如果葉香大人認為這裡很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.20,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,開心 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,開心到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.72,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,博七 打擾一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.83,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那個 盲太郎這人我有些難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.56,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我外出一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.24,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,別忘了是誰救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.33,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,無名的榆木腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:45.04,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒有老闆我哪有你今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,你想說的就是這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好好完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:51.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近她總是莫名其妙地情緒不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.23,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果那東西有一丁點異常馬上向我匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.34,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.31,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你真的知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果你敢背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那個時候可不只是變成蛋羹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:10.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總感覺這條線不是去池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,事到如今還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這種景色給爸媽看一定會被嚇一跳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說不定這只是普通的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,父親是裸鼴鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,母親是樹袋鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 爺爺是三葉蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,圖書館的書忘記還了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,拖欠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,反正又是些奇怪的書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,沒有人會借閱的放心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不行啊玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也不能因為這樣不還啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,慘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看吧 靜留也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只吃了一半的便當盒好像就那樣扔在那沒管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.63,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,多半在 被窩上面 或是裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「裡面」是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就是 那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定你母親會幫你想辦法解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小熊貓在吃之前是會清洗的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.60,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那是浣熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小熊貓是不會洗東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,做飯的時候都會把餐具好好洗乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是什麼奧珀提密斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是指「樂觀主義」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶不是說過車到山前必有路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.48,ZH-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,這個確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有誰能 想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,謝謝你們能一直陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 感覺要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是我們陪著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是我們想來才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 還挺快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等會回去後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在我二十一歲零三個月之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,必須寫出本遊記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊我要讀我要讀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我也會出場的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這可不得不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,記得要寫得酷一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又強又美又聰慧的小實醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,必須真實記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真實 這全部不都是真實的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 不知道還能不能回吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難道喜歡上了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難道不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不過 也不能否定沒有這種可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,肯定回去啊 和葉香一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都在等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,會等著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:03.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,仙人 天鵝船的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,給我們地圖的老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 在那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,失誤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:31.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實快給我拿來繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,列車停下 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.67,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,唉唉真的以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不是沿著池袋線逆流而上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼從池袋那邊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不 我已經越過了吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.61,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,向著吾野西邊的西吾野出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.70,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一直一直向西向西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但你可是從池袋方向過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是在某個地方拐了個大彎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.27,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,還真有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.01,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,地圖給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.27,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,之前我送給你們的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.01,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你們就這樣對待它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟寫得東西也太含糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「拙巧」風格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.68,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這個地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.01,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是現在唯一一個可以展示世界樣貌的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.18,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是智慧的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你們還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.56,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,第一次見面在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.90,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,另外現在在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.72,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,唔 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個難不成是東吾野的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:48.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那這個是武藏橫手的山羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個是稻荷山的小人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,偶然也許也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.80,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這是練愛的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地圖都對上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.70,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,都說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.94,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這是智慧的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在天鵝船上悠哉游哉的旅行之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:06.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓他人信服自己會知道這麼多細節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:10.12,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那麼為什麼遠在134億光年外的星系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.17,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,卻能夠被人類認知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.64,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,探究心啊探究心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.75,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,還有冷靜的觀察力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.55,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我被探究之心所驅使 沿著高麗川逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 原來你說過這些話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.60,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,然而今天為何我們在此相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.41,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,真的是耐人尋味的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是不是在不知道的時候就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實確實 自己做過的事情卻忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,上了年紀腦袋也會變榆木的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.18,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我的腦袋才沒有混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,混亂的東西 是這個世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.77,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼現在你們會是這種表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.96,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,蘑菇 冒牌巨人 僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.14,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,雄偉的高麗川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界確實發生了巨大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但是我想說的 這種變化現在也在繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.12,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個還在繼續變化什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.97,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界在收縮 池袋在膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.56,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界的法則現在在生命的道路上演化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你說的這些也太複雜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,膨脹什麼的 反映與現在不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.85,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不同 是膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.26,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋已經膨脹到變形了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這話讓人感覺不適
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,膨脹起來之後會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:15.93,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.80,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是池袋嗎 那吾野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.21,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,全部都消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,阻止不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.11,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:22.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這麼乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.90,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,城市裡不是有很多大人物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼都不採取措施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大人物是否存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或許他們也從未想到過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不行啊 要好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:35.98,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果有機會早就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這也確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,結果只能靠自己想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.23,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這可說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.34,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不讓這個已經變得混亂的世界更加糟糕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.14,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,總感覺就在池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.53,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你們想要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.13,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,很有可能會與那種可怕的力量對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你們有那樣的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.37,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.47,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,別亂動 乖一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,帽子在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.60,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,在荒蕪的郵政局迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.49,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,請參照滴眼藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,果然不是平時的帽子不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.80,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,龐太郎的軟綿綿手術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,難道再也無法恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.00,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,欸 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G暴走不阻止 池袋也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.25,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,找到7G的根源並停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.53,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,必須要修復這個已然被破壞的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:33.15,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,然後粉碎龐太郎的進一步計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.85,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,必須要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.91,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,稍微回來了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.15,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不對等會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,池袋消失到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.91,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,熵增
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.47,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,宇宙膨脹的迷你版
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.48,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,宇宙大撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,宇宙肥皂泡消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,損壞而消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.79,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,原理暫且不論消滅是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.11,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:00.10,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,可能是明天 也有可能是20億年後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.72,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,誰也無法預測
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.21,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.80,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你說的話一點都不像個技術人員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.99,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,行了行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.23,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.48,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,膨脹消滅 若是無法避免的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是已經不用再冒險了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊很危險的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.28,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,別亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.48,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,無論現在還是未來世界都將在變化之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.29,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,視而不見該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毫無道理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.95,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人生本就毫無道理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:31.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,仙人在7G之前的生活也是荒唐無理的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:31.80,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.65,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一言以蔽之 就是亂七八糟毫無邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋那裡到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不問這些問題才算個成熟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.32,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,智慧的結晶修訂版
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,新的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.06,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.09,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,它會助你們前往池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那這個地圖就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再帶點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們幾個 今後吃的東西也不怎麼缺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,仙人大概挺缺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,接下來去的地方也不能保證不冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.35,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,結果說不定明天又碰見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.69,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界上沒有一件事是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.55,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這句話應該送給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.33,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果你認為膨脹的池袋很安全那就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.35,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,反了反了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,居民們都無法出去 被封控在那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我能夠這樣做只是運氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女王就是「深淵」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,她是由謎團 道路 恐怖所構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女 是葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我不怎麼在意名字早忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香才不會做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:43.46,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人會變 世界也會更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.72,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,難道會存在「絕對同一」的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,存在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.19,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.13,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那也只不過是看起來一樣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.63,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,如果是沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是因為它一直都在運動以保持同一位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.33,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.72,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,沒有什麼是永恆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼最後要說這些討人厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.38,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那就忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:04.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:05.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們都已經聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.97,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,想知道變化的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,還有想要找回不滅的你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.16,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就是因為這樣才有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:18.24,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,在回到有趣的故鄉吾野之前能夠找到西吾野的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.78,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,或是在意想不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:23.16,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,能夠發現西部新宿線和東部東上線的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.95,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那個時候我就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.48,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,擅自瀟灑地離去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.63,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,具體打算要怎麼回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,草餅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那這裡的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,還是說蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然知道你調查了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是仙人你繪畫太微妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我想吃草餅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,紅豆餡
